jQuery HOME :  jQuery is a JavaScript Library. jQuery greatly simplifies JavaScript programming. jQuery is easy to learn.
                $(document).ready(function(){
                  $("p").click(function(){
                    $(this).hide();
                  });
                });
                
jQuery Intro : The purpose of jQuery is to make it much easier to use JavaScript on your website. HTML, CSS, JS를 알고 있어야함

jQuery Get Started : Download the jQuery library from jQuery.com or include jQuery from a CDN, like Google
                     <script src="jquery-3.5.1.min.js"></script> 이렇게 다운받았으면 사용가능
                     <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script> 이거는 CDN
                 
jQuery Syntax : %(selector).action() - $(".text").hide
                
jQuery Selectors : $("p.intro")	Selects all <p> elements with class="intro"
                   $("ul li:first")	Selects the first <li> element of the first <ul>
                   $("ul li:first-child")	Selects the first <li> element of every <ul>
                   $("a[target='_blank']")	Selects all <a> elements with a target attribute value equal to "_blank"
                   $(":button")	Selects all <button> elements and <input> elements of type="button"
                   $("tr:even")	Selects all even <tr> elements
                   
jQuery Events : $("p").click(){function(){ 이런식으로 감. click은 한번 눌렀을때 실행
                dblclick()은 더블클릭시 실행
                mouseenter() 마우스가 그 영역에 들어갔을 때 실행
                mouseleave() 마우스가 그 영역을 떠났을 때 실행
                hover() 이건 mouseenter mouseleave한번에
                mousedown() mouseup()
                focus() blur()
